Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/28/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the upcoming snow storm, new Nicki Minaj music, and the recent Chris Brown allegations.
